Package: ziganka-container-store
Architecture: all
Tag: role::container-store
Description: Ziganka container application store for Cockpit Container Apps
 This package provides the store definition and branding for the Ziganka
 container application store, designed to work with cockpit-container-apps
 on a HALPI2 running HaLOS aboard the sailing vessel Ziganka.
 .
 When installed alongside cockpit-container-apps, it enables a curated view
 of vessel-specific applications: Home Assistant for automation, Music
 Assistant for streaming and local-library playback, a Snapcast client for
 HDMI audio output, and Mayara for marine radar display.
 .
 The store filters packages with the `field::ziganka` debtag.
